black hawk down may refer to :   battle of mogadishu ( 1993 ) , a battle between forces of the united states and somali militia fighters black hawk down ( book ) , a 1999 book by mark bowden about the 1993 battle black hawk down ( film ) , a 2001 film adaptation of bowden 's book , directed by ridley scott black hawk down ( soundtrack ) , the soundtrack to the film of the same name delta force : black hawk down , a 2003 action game based on the events in somalia " blackhawk down " , a song from the 2000 album rancid by the american punk rock band rancid 1994 black hawk shootdown incident , a friendly fire incident over northern iraq   see also black hawk ( disambiguation )

